data.description: Impressive 2-story entry invites you into this delightful 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath home with a loft plus a den! The spacious great room opens to the kitchen with a large island, gas range, new sink, SS appliances, walk-in pantry and a planning area. Primary suite offers 2 walk-in closets, a private bath with double sink vanity and full shower. The 2-car garage has a bump out for extra storage. Step outside to the fully fenced back yard featuring a covered patio and a large expansive stamped patio with a firepit to enjoy on those chilly evenings. The home is located near interstates, shopping, restaurants and HSE schools. Schedule an appt today!
